// MARK: - Onboarding tour
"Skip" = "略過";
"Back" = "返回";
"Next" = "下一步";
"Get Started" = "開始使用";
"Welcome to Owlory" = "歡迎使用 Owlory";
"Your private, local-first command center for everyday life." = "屬於你的私密、本機優先的日常指揮中心。";
"Owlory keeps daily planning, training, writing, career, and home in one place." = "Owlory 將每日計畫、訓練、寫作、事業和家庭集中在一處。";
"Everything stays on your device. There is no account and no sync." = "一切都保留在你的裝置上。沒有帳戶，也沒有同步。";
"This quick tour explains what each tab is for so you know where to start." = "這段快速導覽會說明每個標籤頁的用途，讓你知道從何開始。";
"Your daily command center." = "你的每日指揮中心。";
"Check in with energy, mood, and sleep, then pick up to three focus items for the day." = "記錄精力、心情和睡眠，然後為這一天選出至多三個重點。";
"Continue picks up unfinished work from every other tab so nothing slips silently." = "「繼續」會匯集其他所有標籤頁中未完成的工作，讓任何事都不會悄悄漏掉。";
"End the day with an evening reflection that feeds your weekly digest." = "用一段晚間反思結束一天，它會匯入你的每週摘要。";
"One training session a day, tracked honestly." = "每天一次訓練，如實記錄。";
"Plan today's session, log your readiness, and capture what you actually did." = "規劃今天的訓練，記錄你的狀態，並留下你實際完成的內容。";
"Recurring sessions roll forward automatically when the day changes." = "重複的訓練會在日期變更時自動順延。";
"Reflections can be typed or dictated and stay attached to each session." = "反思可以輸入或口述，並始終附在每次訓練上。";
"A low-friction inbox for unfinished thought." = "用來承接未盡思緒的低門檻收件匣。";
"Capture an idea fast — no folder, tag, or category required." = "快速記下一個想法 — 無需資料夾、標籤或分類。";
"Promote captures into source notes, tasks, or protocols later, only when it helps." = "日後只在有用時，再把記錄提升為來源筆記、任務或協定。";
"Write is forgiving: catch the thought first, sort it never if you like." = "寫作很寬容：先抓住想法，若你願意，永遠不整理也行。";
"Your private record of wins, impact, and stories." = "屬於你的私密記錄，收錄成就、影響與故事。";
"Log wins, impact moments, and interview-ready stories with supporting metrics." = "記錄成就、有影響力的時刻，以及附帶佐證數據、可用於面試的故事。";
"Use it to prep for reviews, recruiter calls, or your next career conversation." = "用它來準備績效評估、招募者來電或下一次職涯對話。";
"Records stay local — nothing is shared unless you choose to export it." = "記錄保留在本機 — 除非你選擇匯出，否則不會分享任何內容。";
"Recurring tasks and household protocols." = "重複任務與家庭協定。";
"Track recurring chores and one-off tasks without losing visibility." = "追蹤重複的家務和一次性任務，不再顧此失彼。";
"Build multi-step protocols for routines like meal prep, travel, or move-out." = "為備餐、出行或搬家等日常，建立多步驟協定。";
"Run a protocol to step through it once, and let Owlory remember the cadence." = "執行一次協定走完所有步驟，讓 Owlory 記住節奏。";
